criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Older adults living independently;

          -  medical approval.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Non-smokers;

          -  Non-morbidly obese;

          -  No history of severe hypertension;

          -  No history of falls;

          -  No orthopaedic, neurological, pulmonary, or cardiac problems.
